OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784047674
OL,3,CWelsh Government set to lose
OL,4,Csupplementary Budget vote
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government is facing defeat
OL,7,Fin a vote on its latest spending plans
OL,8,Fwhich is due to take place in the
OL,9,FSenedd later.
OL,11,FSenedd members will debate and vote on
OL,12,Fthe spending proposals, but as things
OL,13,Fstand, it seems that the Plaid Cymru
OL,14,Fgovernment won't be able to win that
OL,15,Fvote.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/11
