OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784047674
OL,3,CWelsh Government set to lose
OL,4,Csupplementary Budget vote
OL,6,FReform UK Wales and the Welsh
OL,7,FConservatives restated their decision
OL,8,Fnot to back it while Labour has been
OL,9,Fconsidering a 'final offer' from the
OL,10,FWelsh Government but has publicly
OL,11,Fdescribed the offer as 'not enough.'
OL,13,FTalks began after the Plaid Cymru
OL,14,FWelsh Government published its plans
OL,15,Fin its Supplementary Budget, which
OL,16,Fisn't a full budget but rather sets
OL,17,Fout some adjustments in the current
OL,18,Ffinancial year.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
