PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784047674
OL,3,CWelsh Government set to lose
OL,4,Csupplementary Budget vote
OL,6,FIt's not required to spend that money
OL,7,Fin the same areas and the current
OL,8,FPlaid Cymru and previous Labour Welsh
OL,9,FGovernments argued that it didn't all
OL,10,Fneed to be spent on ALN because Wales
OL,11,Ffaces different needs in that sector.
OL,13,FWelsh Labour has been holding out for
OL,14,F#100m to be spent of that money in the
OL,15,Fcurrent financial year.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
